Author Post


07 Aug 2019 23:58






Original article: SCP-577 , by Dr. Kondraki

I chose to rename the article to , which is part of Andrew Lloyd Webber's musical Cats. I felt this title was appropriate, as the song is specifically about reminiscing about the happier past and coming to grips about where you are now, and how your life has lead to this point, and where it will go. That, when combined with the fact that it's from a play about cats made me think it worked perfectly for how I wrote the piece.

Thanks to Unclenicolini, aismallard, zyn, DrMagnus, and probably at least two other people I'm forgetting.

Image Source: https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/02/USS_Pueblo_-_bullet_holes.jpg





